<ab facs="#facs_75_r3l19">ſchıcken vnd <expan>v<ex>er</ex>tigen</expan> / daʒ ſie <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> reiten / daʒ ſie <expan>deſt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ſıchr<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
