</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_75" id="37r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>czog</expan>
<expan>Joh<ex>an</ex></expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>, uns hat der
                            <expan>allerd<ex>ur</ex>hlewhtigist</expan> fürst, unser
                                <expan>gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>, der römisch künig,
                            <expan>verschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz wir unser frewnde czü seinen
                        gnaden schicken süllen, daz die bey im czü
                        <expan>Heydelb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> sein <app><note><q type="date">auf sant Vinczencii tag czenacht
                            nu schirst</q>22.01.1410</note></app>. Und <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz ewr gnade auf
                                <expan>diselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> czeite auch hinab czereiten willen
                        habe. <expan>Dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir uns von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> bey disem <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> an <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> brief wissen
                        lassen wöllet, auf <expan>welich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tag ir ew czü erheben
                        mainet, auf das, daz sich <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> darczü schicken und
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>tigen</expan>, daz sie
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> reiten, daz sie
                            <expan>dest<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>sichr<ex>er</ex></expan> hinabe <expan>küme<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>müge<ex>n</ex></expan>. Das wölle etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Anthonii.</ab>
</div>
